    {
      "voiceId": "scott-galloway",
      "voiceName": "Scott Galloway",
      "platform": "bluesky",
      "text": "We\u2019ve been together for 9 years now. Live in Austin.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://bsky.app/profile/profgalloway.com/post/3mh4f66hn3c2y",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-15T16:42:05.086Z",
      "type": "post"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "scott-galloway",
      "voiceName": "Scott Galloway",
      "platform": "bluesky",
      "text": "\u201cWe\u2019re about to flip Texas.\u201d From our conversation with James Talarico.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://bsky.app/profile/profgalloway.com/post/3mh44sem4x223",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-15T14:12:18.947Z",
      "type": "post"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "scott-galloway",
      "voiceName": "Scott Galloway",
      "platform": "bluesky",
      "text": "A year ago, I predicted the first CEO who forcefully and publicly resisted Trump could reap significant benefits, both reputationally and commercially. \n\nWith its reputation for breaking barriers and the boldness chromosome in its DNA, I thought/hoped it would be Nike. But Dario Amodei just did it.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://bsky.app/profile/profgalloway.com/post/3mh2urph5t22l",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-15T02:16:07.093Z",
      "type": "post"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "scott-galloway",
      "voiceName": "Scott Galloway",
      "platform": "bluesky",
      "text": "Livestream with James Talarico and Jessica Tarlov today in 9 minutes.\n\nMeet us on Substack: open.substack.com/live-stream/...?",
      "sourceUrl": "https://bsky.app/profile/profgalloway.com/post/3mh25n6y77c2v",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-14T19:21:59.541Z",
      "type": "post"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "scott-galloway",
      "voiceName": "Scott Galloway",
      "platform": "bluesky",
      "text": "Live with Ed Elson today at SXSW.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://bsky.app/profile/profgalloway.com/post/3mgzpbjtxtk2p",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-14T15:04:55.900Z",
      "type": "post"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "scott-galloway",
      "voiceName": "Scott Galloway",
      "platform": "bluesky",
      "text": "Livestream tomorrow with @jamestalarico.bsky.social and @jessicatarlov.bsky.social.\n\nMeet us here: open.substack.com/live-stream/...",
      "sourceUrl": "https://bsky.app/profile/profgalloway.com/post/3mgxny2aexs2m",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-13T19:36:24.300Z",
      "type": "post"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "scott-galloway",
      "voiceName": "Scott Galloway",
      "platform": "bluesky",
      "text": "We don\u2019t need a revolution,,, We need a functioning IRS, capital gains taxed as income, and the death of the carried-interest loophole. bit.ly/4blFkfo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://bsky.app/profile/profgalloway.com/post/3mgv7q2szf22j",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-12T20:16:04.634Z",
      "type": "post"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "scott-galloway",
      "voiceName": "Scott Galloway",
      "platform": "bluesky",
      "text": "Iran\u2019s cheap drone advantage. My conversation with Peter Zeihan is out today.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://bsky.app/profile/profgalloway.com/post/3mgutpp2t6s2e",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-12T16:41:07.403Z",
      "type": "post"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "scott-galloway",
      "voiceName": "Scott Galloway",
      "platform": "bluesky",
      "text": "There's no such thing as toxic masculinity \u2014 that\u2019s the emperor of all oxymorons. There\u2019s cruelty, criminality, bullying, predation, and abuse of power. \n\nIf you\u2019re guilty of any of these things, or conflate being male with coarseness and savagery, you\u2019re not masculine; you\u2019re anti-masculine.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://bsky.app/profile/profgalloway.com/post/3mgskpx4ihc2t",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-11T18:54:52.696Z",
      "type": "post"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "scott-galloway",
      "voiceName": "Scott Galloway",
      "platform": "bluesky",
      "text": "America\u2019s CEOs aren\u2019t acting in the interest of shareholders by staying silent about democracy and the rule of law, they\u2019re acting out of fear. www.profgmedia.com/p/role-models",
      "sourceUrl": "https://bsky.app/profile/profgalloway.com/post/3mgsdnjmjtc2k",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-11T16:48:15.241Z",
      "type": "post"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "scott-galloway",
      "voiceName": "Scott Galloway",
      "platform": "bluesky",
      "text": "My thoughts on Sam Altman\u2019s apparent preference for machines over humans, A.I. founders loudly fretting over the technology they created after cashing in and peacing out, and the critiques of my recent book.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://bsky.app/profile/profgalloway.com/post/3mgqt7e3mck2d",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-11T02:21:20.074Z",
      "type": "post"
